Home > Roman Product Range > 
 Welcome to Roman Shower Enclosures
Roman presents the complete showering package, with something to suit every taste, space and budget.
Roman’s extensive range comprehensively covers high quality shower enclosures including walk-ins, everything you need to create a stunningly contemporary wetroom, ingenious bath screens, inward opening, outward opening and sliding door shower enclosures, low-level shower trays and an exclusive range of appealing accessories. Roman has a range to satisfy all your showering needs and our exquisite collection of products are guaranteed to transform any bathroom retreat into a spa like sanctuary. 

